{"tid":2517381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★康怡花園N2座確診外傭　上月18日 已接種首劑復必泰疫苗","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T09:42:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"84304036fe7342e5a94125937591d5f0adbbbef0","tid":2517381,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"本港新增6宗新型肺炎確診，本地及輸入個案各有3宗，包括一名住在鰂魚涌康怡花園N2座的46歲外傭，被列為本地源頭不明個案，她沒有病徵。至於她的朋友，住在薄扶林道豪峰的38歲外傭亦確診。衞生署表示，兩人同時帶有N501Y和E484K變種病毒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，據了解，該名46歲外傭曾於上月18日接種首劑復必泰疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589366-20210505.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589366-20210505.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=ef68a4dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589366-20210505.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b3a03a8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589366-20210505.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8980bff6061a5ee7bed1e2a0a7468d7f2a6497c8","tid":2517381,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fad9be2eb3d15eb5c856c26e2771153285f25e","tid":2517381,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc108281c77023b4230ad2b59